        <section class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center color">
    
    <h2 class="mt-3">{{ selectCocktail.strDrink }}</h2>
    <div class="d-flex mt-5 color  cocktail-indiv">

        <div class="card h-100 color border card-cocktail color">
            <img src="https://img.freepik.com/fotos-gratis/cocktail-de-vista-lateral-em-um-copo-grande_176474-2486.jpg?w=740&t=st=1674571394~exp=1674571994~hmac=dc350191625389c1c2088bd54f0e8b4e25351cc178fe0314debcb3859a883479" class="card-img-top" alt="Hollywood Sign on The Hill"/>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title d-flex justify-content-center fs-2">Moscow Mule</h5>
              <p class="card-text fs-6">
                We could define it as the cocktail par excellence. The Moscow Mule, loaded with freshness, is back in trend from time to time and, although there are numerous variations, the original recipe is always the most popular. Here you can find the original recipe for the Moscow Mule.
              </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="fs-5">
            <li>45 ml of vodka</li>
            <img src="https://img.freepik.com/vetores-gratis/garrafa-de-vodka-com-etiqueta-vermelha_1268-95.jpg?w=740&t=st=1674573774~exp=1674574374~hmac=835a5ff65d53e01dec01254ccff76eaf2039870be59dda2e8195fa8e5bc603d1" alt="" class="ingredient">
